{"tid":146990,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"歐聯　蘇神話只有巴塞可以落後4球翻盤","createTime":"2017-03-07T14:03:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T13:46:50.000Z","uid":18279,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ceeed2c84e55112efadd32a280700950d530bf2b","tid":146990,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:03:55.000Z","msg":"巴塞隆拿喺歐聯16強首回合淨吞巴黎聖日耳門4蛋，幾乎被全世界睇衰佢哋肯定出局，不過巴塞射手蘇亞雷斯深信未絕望，仲號召球迷支持佢哋創造奇迹添：「想要扭轉落後4球嘅局面，的確好難，但咁唔係完全冇可能，如果有球隊可以喺咁嘅情況下逆轉，咁嗰隊肯定係巴塞，我哋有實力，同埋有足夠嘅策略應付所有情況。」事實上，聖日耳門喺次合回陣容不整，其實巴塞又可以試下搏翻身嘅。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20170307/mobile/bkn-20170307103007312-0307_00882_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20170307%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170307103007312-0307_00882_001.html&d=0oBAxbMcX4V1PEKlHKxm0S7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=953285af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20170307/mobile/bkn-20170307103007312-0307_00882_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"94be5faae8a846fa7307f6cd9e79332d27238881","tid":146990,"uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:07:04.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴都未出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfafa3ac6fd1fd1546a5ff188e4c9f796a025757","tid":146990,"uid":72946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:40:53.000Z","msg":"慢慢試啦 失敗最多咪專注西波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又唔會死既"},{"pid":"822970dd4c8de92802412f453ebb7827d16ab92c","tid":146990,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:41:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f0ec8e276acf86e0d78eaf3fbb4824a73cf0ad","tid":146990,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:43:29.000Z","msg":"你以為自己係阿仙奴咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec8e85e